title: Can not rendered UI with react and react-dom 16.1.1
body:
This is my code:

```js
import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import { Router, Route, hashHistory} from 'react-router'

import Archives from './modules/Archives';
import Layout from './modules/Layout';
import Featured from './modules/Featured';
import Settings from './modules/Settings';
console.log('hi');
ReactDOM.render((
    <Router history={hashHistory}>
        <Route exact path='/' component={Layout}>
            <Route exact path='/featured' component={Featured}/>
            <Route exact path='/archives/:id' name='archives' component={Archives}/>
            <Route exact path='/settings' name='settings' component={Settings}/>
            </Route>
    </Router>
    ),document.getElementById('app'));
```
